display.Name: §c§lVein Seeker

Lore: §r§7Increases §c❁ Strength, §9☣ Crit Chance, §9☠ Crit Damage, §a❈ Defense, and §c❤ Health §7statistics gain by §a5% §7while in the Crystal Hollows.

display.Name: §c§lMole
Lore: §r§7When mining hard stone, you have a §a50%§7 chance to mine §a1§7 adjacent hard stone block.

display.Name: §c§lManiac Miner
Lore: §r§7Spends all your Mana and grants §a+1 §6⸕ Mining Speed §7for every 10 Mana spent, for §a10s§7.
§r§8Pickaxe Abilities apply to all of your pickaxes. You can select a Pickaxe Ability from your Heart of the Mountain.

display.Name: §c§lSky Mall
Lore: §r§7Every SkyBlock day, you receive a random buff in the §2Dwarven Mines§7.
§r§8 ■ §7Gain §a+15% §7chance to gain extra Powder while mining.

display.Name: §c§lMining Madness
Lore: §r§cRequires Luck of the Cave, Seasoned Mineman or Goblin Killer.

Lore: §r§7When mining ores, you have a §a0.21%§7 chance to get a random amount of experience orbs.

display.Name: §c§lFront Loaded

display.Name: §c§lPrecision Mining

display.Name: §c§lDaily Powder
Lore: §r§7Gain §a400 Powder §7from the first ore you mine every day. Works for all Powder types.

display.Name: §c§lCrystallized
Lore: §r§7Grants §a+20 §6⸕ Mining Speed §7and a §a20% §7chance to deal §a+1 §7extra damage near §5Fallen Stars§7.

display.Name: §cReset Heart of the Mountain
